Name: Led It Rain VR
About the game: Led It Rain VR is firstpersonshooter motorcycle driving racing game. Motorcycles, guns, monsters and bikini-babes. Faster you drive and shoot monsters more score you obtain. Monsters include zombies, skeletons, werewolves, chainsaw-maniacs and hilarious Wheelchair Zombiesᵀᴹ. Led It Rain features music by Electric Deathbeat and a theme song by Maze of Jesse Lane.
